rows.label: qst700105_msg0001
rows.name:
We've come to get you.
Let's go together, okay?

rows.label: qst700105_msg0101
rows.name: We mean you no harm. Rest easy.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0201
rows.name:
You must be Ajijii-san.
It's all right now.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0202
rows.name: Come, let's return to your master.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0301
rows.name: There you are. You look well.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0302
rows.name:
Uh, Sababaa...? No,
Ajijii? Time to go home.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0402
rows.name:
All right? You're coming
with me quietly.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0501
rows.name: You there... you're Ajijii, aren't you?

rows.label: qst700105_msg0502
rows.name: Your master is waiting. Let's go.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0602
rows.name:
Sorry to startle you. Shall
we go home together?

rows.label: qst700105_msg0702
rows.name: The chase is over. Let's go home.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0801
rows.name:
I am glad. Above all,
that you are safe.

rows.label: qst700105_msg0802
rows.name:
I am Wadatsumi, and I am
your ally. Come, this way.
